a1c50dba8b","tid":1077980,"uid":94454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/920/736/619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F920%2F736%2F619.jpg&h=4492df5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08df6a3e2aa009099eb45343f52addd9d650e80c","tid":1077980,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180224/57866666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F57866666&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=b20daf60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F57866666&h=1d8a425e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180224/57866666</a>"},{"pid":"f82a4c70957225fa0e9731c86379fa1455b4c26d","tid":1077980,"uid":41423,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"一、剷青 Short back and sides<br />\n－這是最常見的髮型之一，兩旁是整齊地剷短，而頭頂就留有長度，有點像正方形形狀。<br />\n二、偷薄 Thin out<br />\n－由厚髮變成薄髮。<br />\n三、修一修 Trim<br />\n－如果客人要求trim，他們通常都是滿意自己的髮型，只是想保持頭髮形狀。<br />\n四、剪短 Cut short<br />\n－想剪多短呢？<br />\n五、剪碎 Layering<br />\n－是用作製造頭髮自然蓬鬆的效果。<br />\n六、鬢髮（的水）Sideburns<br />\n－視乎你想鬢髮高點或低點，higher or lower。<br />\n七、漸層髮型 Fade<br />\n－可以是skin fade，即是由皮膚開始漸層，又或是1mm fade，由1mm開始漸層。"},{"pid":"25edf35cc9d5408d6ebeb1e0f15b219a5b83a1cf","tid":1077980,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"Cut all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}